	<h1 class="title">男神肖恩·潘专访大毒枭的故事，值得拍成一部电影啊！｜好奇心人类学</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Ravi Somaiya</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-12 13:13:08 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/20577/medium/20577.png?1452571254" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


